@gateway = http://localhost:8080

### Gateway health
GET {{gateway}}/gateway/health

### Gateway routes
GET {{gateway}}/gateway/routes

### Forward auth register
POST {{gateway}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "gateway_user",
  "email": "gateway_user@example.com",
  "password": "pass1234",
  "fullName": "Gateway User",
  "role": "READER"
}

### Forward posts
GET {{gateway}}/posts/published

### Forward comments
GET {{gateway}}/comments/post/1

### Forward newsletter
GET {{gateway}}/newsletter/subscribers

### Forward notifications
GET {{gateway}}/notifications/recipient/1
